Package: duoNovo
Title: DuoNovo: Identifying De Novo Variants from Single Parent-Proband Duos Using Long-Read Sequencing
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Leandros", "Boukas", email = "leandrosboukas@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
     , person("Seth", "Berger", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: DuoNovo identifies de novo variants from single parent-proband duos using long-read sequencing data. 
    By reconstructing haplotypes and detecting identical-by-descent blocks, DuoNovo classifies candidate variants 
    (heterozygous in the proband; absent in the parent) as de novo or inherited from the non-sequenced parent.
